  • java.lang.Object
    • inra.ijpb.morphology.GeodesicReconstruction3DTest

  • public class GeodesicReconstruction3DTest
extends java.lang.Object
    Test the various static methods in GeodesicReconstruction3D class. Many tests are already performed in geodrec subpackage, but this class tests only global behavious, whereas geodrec focus on differences between algorithms.
